{"tid":1420131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重點］民間記者會話唔係大台，但係確實係","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:37:01.000Z","uid":296931,"like":10,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d231234da03e77fab24ac166b7b0581d74b3635c","tid":1420131,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">首先我真係好感動，因為首次見到有民間記者會辦得成！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n但就算講咗唔係代表所有人，記者會個效果實然上都代表咗<br />\n話冇代表其實係有<br />\n不如承認啦好嗎<br />\n連登仔女連承認呢樣嘢都冇勇氣 點對得住勇武嘅宗旨</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1d94dfaf0d991f8c5d345c4b4fbf24546e6a2c","tid":1420131,"uid":296931,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8a5796df5be44e52e408e68289e6f184eafd52ab","tid":1420131,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"今次只係第一步！"},{"pid":"739be12419bc268f3f4adec29146f8f4de3819af","tid":1420131,"uid":48143,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n跟本就唔係<br />\n我係連登仔，但佢冇代表我喎<br />\n我上去講既野就好唔同<br />\n所以佢並非大台<br />\n<br />\n就好似你P牌上去講野都唔代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f8f9ecd7e60c88330d0dfe6e758d5e3cfae713","tid":1420131,"uid":253170,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"明唔明點解話要無大台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗清楚先啦<br />\n<br />\n係咪想d 狗同柒婆直接搵佢開刀呀"},{"pid":"df5c15cfc664666a7676384f0c0c7c252cae492d","tid":1420131,"uid":76680,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"唔